column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: MILKA CHOCOLATE BISCUIT TABLET MILK WITH BISCUIT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210289285
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, vegetable fats (palm, palm kernel), WHEAT flour, skimmed MILK powder, cocoa butter, whey powder (from MILK), cocoa mass, MILK fat, fat-reduced cocoa powder (1%), WHEAT starch, glucose syrup, emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), HAZELNUT paste, raising agents (potassium hydrogen carbonate, ammonium hydrogen carbonate, sodium hydrogen carbonate), salt, flavourings.7,5% skimmed milk powder in the filling. Milk chocolate contains: Cocoa solids 30% minimum. Milk solids 18% minimum. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 12/28/2016
